<br>
Amplification is a song that makes all songs WHILE it is cast last 5 ticks instead of 3, thus allowing you to stack 4 songs easily (including itself).  BoH is a clicky sword  that has effect Niv's that lasts 3 ticks like all other bard songs.  Using this you can get 5 songs + amplification.<br>
