<br>
1. Cassindra's Chorus of Clarity/Selo's Song of Travel<br>
2. Cantata of Replenishment<br>
3. Amplification<br>
4. Verses of Victory/Villa's Verses of Celerity<br>
5. Brusco's Boastful Bellow/Largo's Absonent Binding<br>
6. Brusco's Bombastic Bellow/Katta's Song of Sword Dancing<br>
7. Song of Twilight<br>
